### Download Group NDJSON
# The attribution Group resource with its full member list.
# Each line is a complete FHIR Group resource in JSON format.
# Prerequisite: Run the Bulk Export Workflow first.

GET {{groupFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200

### Download Patient NDJSON
# All Patient resources attributed to the Group.
# Each line is a complete FHIR Patient resource in JSON format.

GET {{patientFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200

### Download Coverage NDJSON
# Coverage resources linking patients to their insurance plans.
# Each line is a complete FHIR Coverage resource in JSON format.

GET {{coverageFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200

### Download RelatedPerson NDJSON
# Persons related to attributed patients (e.g. guardians).
# Each line is a complete FHIR RelatedPerson resource in JSON format.

GET {{relatedPersonFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200

### Download Practitioner NDJSON
# Healthcare practitioners linked to the attribution group.
# Each line is a complete FHIR Practitioner resource in JSON format.

GET {{practitionerFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200

### Download PractitionerRole NDJSON
# Role assignments linking practitioners to organizations.
# Each line is a complete FHIR PractitionerRole resource in JSON format.

GET {{practitionerRoleFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200

### Download Organization NDJSON
# Payer and provider organizations in the attribution group.
# Each line is a complete FHIR Organization resource in JSON format.

GET {{organizationFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200

### Download Location NDJSON
# Physical locations where care is delivered.
# Each line is a complete FHIR Location resource in JSON format.

GET {{locationFileUrl}}
Accept: application/fhir+ndjson

?? status == 200
